陸人黎 <br />\n而今日果班人絕對唔似係平時啲大媽旅行團<br />\n果堆人全部係男人 20歲到40歲都有<br />\n都唔似家族/朋友關係黎香港玩<br />\n望落都唔係咩好人 有紋身<br />\n全部唔知講咩話 唔係廣東話 唔係普通話 都唔似客家話<br />\n全部人冇人拖行理 都係輕裝<br />\n而佢地一見到車廂電視播反送中新聞都好留意<br />\n全部人唔似平時啲大媽黎旅行有講有笑<br />\n雖然我聽唔明佢地講咩話<br />\n但清楚聽到有人講個&quot;斬&quot;字大聲左<br />\n其他人都立即語態上叫佢細聲啲<br />\n<br />\n我落車前錄低左部份人士樣貌<br />\n有人見我錄影問我做咩<br />\n然後全部大迴避鏡頭而且細聲討論<br />\n<br />\n而佢地大部份人全程都係睇住佢地一個wechat群組<br />\n群名大約係 香港旅行團<br />\n入面全部係錄音 <br />\n我係太和站落左車 佢地繼續住9龍方向<br />\n9:05分 報左警 大埔警區聯絡左我了解<br />\n<br />\n報檔編號<br />\nTPRM 190 26109"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8X9xbjV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8X9xbjV.png&h=a152984d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kRYepEX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkRYepEX.jpg&h=9b53f362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bEnnyyi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbEnnyyi.jpg&h=c296bf80&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iODxVMF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiODxVMF.jpg&h=ee696623&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g0mC6Tn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg0mC6Tn.jpg&h=cdb23e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xzoh6Tp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxzoh6Tp.jpg&h=5af1f498&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcrfMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcrfMM.png&h=e19d7a0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kC4UpE8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkC4UpE8.png&h=c1230262&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Zp9dyv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Zp9dyv.png&h=551f3100&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOkkkdx.jpg